@{FG Highlight}Information on Soft-Logik Products@{FG Text}

@{FG Highlight}PageStream 3.0: desktop publisher@{FG Text}
-Put text and graphics on paper in anyway imaginable.

@{FG Highlight}TypeSmith 2.5: font editor@{FG Text}
- Convert, create, and edit PostScript, TrueType, Compugraphic Intellifont
  and Soft-Logik DMF fonts.

@{FG Highlight}Wordworth 3.1: word processor@{FG Text}
- Write letters, reports, essays, and books.

@{FG Highlight}Datastore 1.0: personal database@{FG Text}
- Keep track of names, addresses, home inventory, recipes, and more.

