@node LEGL "License, Copyrights, Trademarks and Credits"

@{FG Highlight}License, Copyrights, Trademarks and Credits@{FG Text}

@{FG Highlight}Copyright@{FG Text}

Copyright 1988-1995 Soft-Logik Publishing Corporation. All rights reserved.

No part of this program, help system or documentation may be reproduced,
