@{FG Highlight}Trademarks@{FG Text}

PageStream, TypeSmith, Art Expression, PageLiner, BME and Soft-Logik are
trademarks or registered trademarks of Soft-Logik Publishing Corporation.
Amiga, AmigaDOS and Workbench are registered trademarks of Commodore-Amiga,
Inc. Macintosh is a trademark of Apple Computer Inc. MS-DOS and Windows are
